4G/LTE Module
----------------

|Product| is equipped with a **mini-PCIe connector** that can connect to a 4G/LTE module.
The customer will also need a SIM Card Holder and a 4G/LTE Antenna Connector to ensure 4G/LTE works on the |product|. SIM card does **NOT** support hot plug. **Power off** before inserting or removing SIM card.

.. figure:: /Media/ARM/A9/Others/4G_module.jpg
   :align: center
   :figclass: align-center

   *4G/LTE Module*


.. figure:: /Media/ARM/A9/Others/4G_com.jpg
   :align: center
   :figclass: align-center

   *SIM Card Holder and 4G/LTE Antenna Connector*

.. rst-class:: text-center

   .. image:: /Media/ARM/A9/Others/PPC-A9-101-SIM.jpg
      :align: center
      :width: 640

   *SIM Card Direction*

.. attention::

    The product does not come shipped with the 4G/LTE module by default.
    
